.\" ============================================================================
.Sh HISTORY
Atom was first developed in 2008 by GitHub founder
.An Chris Wanstrath Pq Sy @defunkt ,
originally under the name
.Dq Atomicity .
It was open-sourced in May 2014 along with its application framework,
thence called
.Dq Atom Shell .
The latter was renamed
.Dq Electron
on April 23, 2015.
.
.Pp
On December 15, 2022, Atom was officially discontinued,
its project repositories archived,
and its website redirected to an end-of-life announcement on GitHub's blog.
At the time, its last release was v1.63.1
.Pq published November 23, 2022 .
This release was redacted on January 30, 2023,
following the exposure of encrypted code-signing certificates \
used to sign v1.63.1 and v1.60.0.
Since the redaction,
the last releases published to Atom's stable and beta channels,
respectively, are v1.60.0 and v1.61.0-beta0
.Pq both published on March 8, 2022 .
.
